subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Hawaii quarterback Colt Brennan broke the N.C.A.A. single-season record for touchdown passes Sunday, throwing five in a 41-24 victory over Arizona State in the Hawaii Bowl to push his total to 58.
